？？？<br />\n<br />\n所以就算耶穌既教導，毒撚返到教會都係比人排，返得唔開心最後離教。"},{"pid":"3f7ab60f621a6fef0b15f94c1c326472d2253423","tid":2122934,"uid":329324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"67f2b99440baaf6efcc8b6910d01f69b02b01311","tid":2122934,"uid":151523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:46:19.000Z","msg":"返教會同信教係兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申有返但信就開始不了<br />\n<br />\n其實係見識下冇壞 ，毒撚更加係脫毒既好開始"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:54:37.000Z","msg":"定會唔會天水圍既教會最岩毒撚返？<br />\n<br />\n因為天水圍都係低下階層比較多，相對之下毒撚無咁自卑。"},{"pid":"f10c31eea27a921a1b5adceb554e9444ca2c9022","tid":2122934,"uid":151523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T04:03:58.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪返完教會比人hurt <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老實講 我都試過 <br />\n但每個教會都會有人既問題 <br />\n建議你搵第間 <br />\n解開你既心結"},{"pid":"6bdd9f4ee318ec8bdb7dae85683e10a3216744a8","tid":2122934,"uid":189015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f7ab60f621a6fef0b15f94c1c326472d2253423","tid":2122934,"uid":329324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"67f2b99440baaf6efcc8b6910d01f69b02b01311","tid":2122934,"uid":151523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:46:19.000Z","msg":"返教會同信教係兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申有返但信就開始不了<br />\n<br />\n其實係見識下冇壞 ，毒撚更加係脫毒既好開始"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:54:37.000Z","msg":"定會唔會天水圍既教會最岩毒撚返？<br />\n<br />\n因為天水圍都係低下階層比較多，相對之下毒撚無咁自卑。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"信徒都係人啫，都係一樣會犯罪<br />\n唔需要自卑嘅<br />\n<br />\n唔鐘意同人講嘢咪同人講清楚"},{"pid":"95d9cf05bbf712c68452af124e1e09cc8ba17247","tid":2122934,"uid":147856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T04:05:24.000Z","msg":"溝到番教會既女係唔係拖手拖到結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448b2ff0626fe8aabaf8b3392c884a3d15cf688d","tid":2122934,